snippet: SECOND DAY. A very much larger attendance of clergy and laity marked the assembly of the Convention this morning; and the galleries wee pretty closely filled with the crowd drawn to the exciting spectacle of an Episcopal election....
lead_paragraph: SECOND DAY. A very much larger attendance of clergy and laity marked the assembly of the Convention this morning; and the galleries wee pretty closely filled with the crowd drawn to the exciting spectacle of an Episcopal election.
